<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:197'>欽定四庫全書　　　　　經部四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='197:220'>　周禮詳解　　　　　　禮類一<span class='krp-note'>周禮之屬/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='220:226'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='226:252'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案周禮詳解四十卷宋王昭禹撰陳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='252:275'>　　　　振孫書録解題曰昭禹未詳何等人近世為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='275:298'>　　　　舉子業者多用之其學皆宗王氏新説王與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='298:321'>　　　　之作周禮訂義類編姓氏世次列于龜山楊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='321:344'>　　　　氏之後曰字光逺亦不詳其爵里當為徽欽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='344:370'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='370:393'>　　　　時人今按其書解惟王建國云業格于上下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='393:416'>　　　　謂之王或而圍之謂之國解匪頒之式云散</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='416:439'>　　　　其所藏曰匪以等級之曰頒故匪從匚從非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='439:462'>　　　　言其分而非藏也頒從分從頁言自上而頒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='462:485'>　　　　之下解圃曰園有衆甫謂之圃解鮑魚曰魚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='485:507'>　　　　之鮮者包以致之解鱐曰魚之乾者肅以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='507:530'>　　　　致之解司徒云于文反后為司盖后從一從</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='530:560'>　　　　口從<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1763' title='KR1763' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1763.png'/>從口則所以出命司反之則守令而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='560:586'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='586:609'>　　　　已從一則所以一衆司反之則分衆以治之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='609:639'>　　　　而已從<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR1763' title='KR1763' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR1763.png'/>則承上世之庇覆以君天下司反</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='639:662'>　　　　之則以君之爵為執事之法而已其附㑹穿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='662:685'>　　　　鑿皆遵王氏字説葢當時三經新義列在學</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='685:708'>　　　　官功令所懸故昭禹因之不改然其發明義</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='708:731'>　　　　㫖則有不盡同于王氏之學者如解泉府以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='731:754'>　　　　國服為之息云各以共所服國事賈物為息</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='754:777'>　　　　若農以粟米工以器械皆以其所有也周之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='777:803'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='803:826'>　　　　衰不能為民正田制地税歛無度又從而貸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='826:849'>　　　　之則凶年饑嵗無以為償矣下無以償上之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='849:872'>　　　　人又必責之則稱貸之法豈特無補于民哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='872:895'>　　　　求以國服為之息恐收還其毋而不得葢已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='895:918'>　　　　目睹青苖之弊而隂破其説矣至其闡發經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='918:941'>　　　　義有足訂註疏之誤者如解載師里布屋粟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='941:964'>　　　　謂國宅無征民居有征無布以其不毛使之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='964:987'>　　　　有里布民出耕在田廬入居在里其屋有田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='987:1013'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='1013:1036'>　　　　以出粟今不耕田則計屋而歛之謂之屋粟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1036:1059'>　　　　不從先儒以里布為二十五家之泉屋粟為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1059:1082'>　　　　三夫之粟又解近郊十一逺郊二十而三甸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1082:1105'>　　　　稍縣都皆無過十二因當時正役後因逺近</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1105:1128'>　　　　劇易而制云云皆為先儒所未發故宋人釋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1128:1151'>　　　　周禮者如王與之訂義林之竒講義多引其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1151:1174'>　　　　説固不得以遵用新説而盡廢之也五官皆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1174:1197'>　　　　不載叙官元末朱申作句解葢從其例究為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1197:1223'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-3b' );" name="000-3b" class="pb">[000-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1223:1246'>　　　　一失今姑仍舊本録之内附載陸徳明釋文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1246:1269'>　　　　而卷首以徳明之名冠昭禹前今攷昭禹自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1269:1292'>　　　　序末云因釋文而作則釋文或後人所増入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1292:1315'>　　　　又以徳明時代在前遂題諸昭禹上歟今仍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1315:1338'>　　　　録其音釋而徳明之名則附著于此不復並</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1338:1359'>　　　　列簡端焉乾隆四十六年六月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1359:1391'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1391:1417'>　　　　　　　　　　總　校　官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸　費　墀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1437:1463'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-4a' );" name="000-4a" class="pb">[000-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1463:1471'>周禮詳解原序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1471:1494'>道判為萬物之成理理之成具不説之大法禮者法之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1494:1517'>大分道實寓焉聖人循道之序以制禮制而用之則存</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1517:1540'>乎法推而行之則存乎人其人足以任官其官足以行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1540:1563'>法然後禮之事舉矣故唐虞稽古建官惟百夏商官倍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1563:1586'>至周增而為三百六十非故好詳也王者之世物繁事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1586:1609'>衆其制不得不然也孔子曰周監於二代郁郁乎文哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1609:1632'>吾從周盖言盛矣然道之常無下散於常有之域法象</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1632:1658'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-4b' );" name="000-4b" class="pb">[000-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1658:1681'>而為天地變通而為四時聖人體道之常無以觀其妙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1681:1704'>體道之常有以觀其微其精至於與天地合其徳與四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1704:1727'>時合其序雖先天而天且弗違尚何事於仰觀俯法然</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1727:1750'>後奉其時哉惟夫出神天之本宗應帝王之興起天地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1750:1773'>固有大美矣四時固有眀法矣雖聖人烏得而違焉是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1773:1796'>故因天地之大美逹而為治教因四時之明法達而為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1796:1819'>禮政刑事然則常無之道為萬物而有天地四時聖人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1819:1842'>為天下而有治教禮政刑事天地四時道之所任以致</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1842:1868'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-5a' );" name="000-5a" class="pb">[000-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1868:1891'>其用者也六官聖人任以致其事者也噫六官之建豈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1891:1914'>聖人之私智哉實天理之所為也由此以觀則禮之事</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1914:1937'>雖顯於形名度數之粗而禮之理實隠於道徳性命之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1937:1960'>微即事而幽者闡即理而顯者微然則禮其神之所為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1960:1983'>乎夫神無在而無乎不在無為而無乎不為聖人立禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1983:2006'>以為體行禮以為翼事為之制曲為之防亦神之無不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='2006:2029'>在無不為之意也彼荀卿徒知禮為道之華而不知為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='2029:2052'>物之致乃曰生於聖人之偽又烏知禮意哉王昭禹光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='2052:2078'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-5b' );" name="000-5b" class="pb">[000-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2078:2082'>逺序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2082:2085'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2085:2088'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2088:2091'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2091:2094'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2094:2097'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2097:2100'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2100:2109'>　周禮詳解原序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2133:2159'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-6a' );" name="000-6a" class="pb">[000-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2159:2167'>周禮互註總括</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2167:2179'>經禮三百<span class='krp-note'>記禮/器</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2179:2204'>經禮謂周禮也周禮六篇其官有三百六十<span class='krp-note'>上文/註</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2204:2227'>文武所以綱紀百官君臨天下周公定之致隆平龍鳯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2227:2252'>之瑞然則周禮起於成帝劉歆成於鄭𤣥<span class='krp-note'>春官/疏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2252:2279'>鄭𤣥以為括囊大典網羅衆家是以周禮盛行<span class='krp-note'>上文/同</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2279:2298'>韓子所見葢周之舊典禮經也<span class='krp-note'>左/序</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2298:2321'>齊仲孫歸曰不去慶父魯難未已公曰若之何而去之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2321:2347'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-6b' );" name="000-6b" class="pb">[000-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2347:2370'>對曰難不已將自斃君其待之公曰魯可取乎對曰不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2370:2397'>可猶秉周禮周禮所以本也魯不棄周禮未可動也<span class='krp-note'>閔/元</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2397:2403'><span class='krp-note'>年/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2403:2426'>晉侯使韓宣子來聘且告為政而來見禮也觀書於太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2426:2449'>史氏見易象與魯春秋曰周禮盡在魯矣吾乃今知周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2449:2467'>公之徳與周之所以王也<span class='krp-note'>昭二/年</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2467:2484'>或問周官曰立事<span class='krp-note'>揚子重/黎篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2484:2507'>子居家不暫捨周禮門人問子子曰先師以王道極是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2507:2533'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-7a' );" name="000-7a" class="pb">[000-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2533:2556'>也如有用我執此以徃通也宗周之介也敢忘其禮乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2556:2576'>子曰周禮其敵於天命<span class='krp-note'>文中子/魏相篇</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2576:2595'>周公典禮與天命齊其長久<span class='krp-note'>上文/註</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2595:2618'>唐太宗問三代損益何者為當魏徴對曰孔子曰周監</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2618:2641'>於二代郁郁乎文哉吾從周周禮周公旦所裁詩書仲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2641:2664'>尼所述雖綱紀頺缺而節制具焉荀孟陳之於前董伸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2664:2687'>之於後遺談餘義可舉而行若擇前代憲章發明王道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2687:2710'>臣請以周典唯所施行上大悦翌日又召徴入上曰朕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2710:2736'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-7b' );" name="000-7b" class="pb">[000-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2736:2759'>昨夜讀周禮真聖作也首篇云惟王建國辨方正位體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2759:2782'>國經野設官分職以為民極誠哉深乎良久謂徵曰朕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2782:2810'>思之不井田不封建而欲行周公之道不可得也<span class='krp-note'>録唐/論禮</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2810:2817'><span class='krp-note'>欒/事</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2817:2837'>凡禮十三家五百五十五篇<span class='krp-note'>前藝/文志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2837:2860'>帝王質文世有損益至周曲為之防事為之制故曰禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2860:2883'>經三百威儀三千及周之衰諸侯將踰法度惡其害已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2883:2895'>皆滅去其籍<span class='krp-note'>同/上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2895:2921'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-8a' );" name="000-8a" class="pb">[000-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2921:2941'>周公所制百官品物備於此矣<span class='krp-note'>晉禮/志</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2941:2964'>沈峻尤長三禮陸倕徐勉書薦峻曰凡聖賢所講之書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2964:2990'>必以周官立義則周官一書實為羣經源本<span class='krp-note'>南史/本傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='2990:3013'>褚無量建議禮文雖衆莫如周禮周禮者周公致太平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3013:3036'>之書先聖極折衷之典法天地而行教化辨方位而叙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3036:3060'>人倫其義可以幽贊神明其文可以經緯邦國備物致用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3060:3072'>其可忽乎<span class='krp-note'>唐本/傳</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3072:3095'>周禮儀禮並周公所記所謂禮經三百威儀三千禮經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3095:3121'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0005', 'WYG', '000-8b' );" name="000-8b" class="pb">[000-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3121:3140'>則周禮也威儀則儀禮也<span class='krp-note'>三禮/正義</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3140:3163'>周禮遭秦滅學藏於山巖屋壁以故不亡漢武有李氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3163:3186'>獲之以上河間獻王獨闕冬官一篇求之千金不得乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3186:3209'>以考工記補之遂奏入於秘府時儒以為非是不行至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3209:3232'>劉歆獨識其書為周公致太平之跡始奏立學官後鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3232:3244'>𤣥為之註<span class='krp-note'>同/上</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3244:3247'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3247:3256'>　周禮互註總括</span><br/>
